{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Map2.gif?t=1730769325\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Korea Dynasty</h2>The Joseon Dynasty ruled the Korean Peninsula from the 14th to the 20th century.<br><br>Korea was a centralized bureaucratic and Confucian state. And in terms of grographical location, it survived through diplomacy and war with great powers and successfully made outstanding cultures such as Hangeul as well as advanced science and technology.<br><br>On the other hand, there was inequality due to the strict status system, and there were so many people who starved even if they worked every day.<br><br>This game is an exploration and survival game composed of open world and contents by reconstructing the culture and geography of the Korea Dynasty.<br><br>You will begin as the slave of the Joseon Dynasty who learns survival skills, buys or steals identity to escape from a chased life.<br><br>Players can be a bandit, merchant, craftsman, bureaucrat or even explorer who search for historical sites in the whole world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Door.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br>The lands of morning calm will be open! What would you choose?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to this game!</h2><br>This game is a survival/life game where you freely roam around a world recreated based on the culture of the Joseon Dynasty.<br><br>Here, you can draw a national map based on the actual topography of the Korean Peninsula, and travel anywhere on the Korean Peninsula.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Sky.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br>How will your future be written in a world where you have to do whatever you can, be it malicious, good, or intentional action in order to survive?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Ship.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- 3000\u33a2 of open world, natural environment and islands</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Castle.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- Various cities and castles</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Horse.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- More than 600 items and production methods from the Joseon Dynasty, including consumables, equipment, clothing, etc.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Build.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- Joseon Dynasty style building system</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Heritage.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- More than a hundred relics of the Joseon Dynasty</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216600/extras/Store.gif?t=1730769325\" /><br><strong>- Quests, social influence with NPCs</strong><br><br><strong>- A trade system that allows you to make money using special products</strong><br><br><strong>- Co-op multiplayer</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Joseon barbecue.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2216600/25c70cd60f6330a0f06cba6732464b59b3879188.jpg"},{"name":"Sleep is a medicine.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2216600/8b06c6618852fe5f3a27bce72356623e6ff90c81.jpg"},{"name":"As you sow, so you shall reap.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2216600/67b80e191fe99b5039eec5c4cda538f2f5109e7b.jpg"},{"name":"Map knows the way.",